Special provisions for California residents under the CCPA; and
Special provisions for EEA residents under the GDPR.
By providing clear and detailed information about NeoCharge's data practices, this Privacy Statement helps build trust with users and ensures compliance with applicable privacy laws and regulations. It is important to regularly review and update the Privacy Statement to reflect any changes in NeoCharge's data practices or applicable laws.